Package net.proteusframework.processes.form Description

Data model for dynamic forms. Forms can have many types of fields and may be configured by an advanced user. FormDefinition is the root configuration object, which may have may have several FormRevisions, each of which may have several FormViews. A FormView is displayed to a user, and data is captured into a FormProcess. Use FormDAO to retrieve form objects. See the "ui" subpackage for details on displaying or editing FormDefinition and FormProcess.
